author: Dan Ripley For Mailonline
title: Wolves vs Chelsea, FA Cup fifth round, LIVE | Daily Mail Online
text: comments Wolves go in search of a second major Premier League scalp of the season this weekend when Chelsea visit Molineux in the FA Cup. Paul Lambert's side, who sprung a major surprise in round four by knocking out Liverpool at Anfield, could not ask for a more difficult test against the champions elect. The Blues arrive in the West Midlands having seen off Brentford and are hot favourites to progress. Keep up-to-date with all the action with Sportsmail's live updates, with ROB DRAPER and LAURIE WHITWELL in place at Molineux. Please wait, coming soon
